ĻNorman Long
5 May 1933 - 15 May 2005.
Lyme Regis was Norman's most favourite place in the whole world,
his ashes lay out in the bay, his spirit still roaming the beach
and remembered here now on the Cobb.
Loved and missed by all."¾
